textAfterTable: 21 Songs Album Review GNP's Greatest Hits is a fairly good collection of all the prime Dick Dale material — "King of the Surf Guitar," "Let's Go Trippin'," "Miserlou," "Death of a Gremmie" — but it's been supplanted by Rhino's superior, definitive single-disc King of the Surf Guitar.
